parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power and acceleration, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission service urgent light illuminates
the vehicle jerks or hesitates when shifting gears
the vehicle will not shift into gear
the vehicle will only shift into third gear
and a high-pitched noise or grinding sound is heard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transfer case can cause the vehicle to lose power and acceleration, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: the vehicle will not shift into gear
and a grinding or whining noise is heard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The coolant leak into the transmission can cause the transmission to fail, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission service urgent light illuminates
and the vehicle will not shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the instrument panel can cause the driver to lose critical information about the vehicle's speed, fuel level, and other essential systems, leading to potential accidents or safety risks.
symptoms: The instrument panel lights stop illuminating
and there is no light; the SRS airbag light comes on; the radio stops working.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various safety-critical systems to malfunction, leading to potential accidents or safety risks.
symptoms: The windshield wipers come on automatically; the battery light and electrical warning side come on; the power steering and air conditioning are affected.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water ingress can cause electrical system failures, corrosion, and other safety issues, leading to potential accidents or safety risks.
symptoms: Water drains onto the front passenger floor and occasionally the driver's side after it rains; musty smell from frequent water in the vehicle; CD player malfunction; short in the electrical system causing battery replacement.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Clogged sunroof drain tubes can cause water to accumulate and lead to electrical system failures, corrosion, and other safety issues, leading to potential accidents or safety risks.
symptoms: Water drains onto the front passenger floor and occasionally the driver's side after it rains; musty smell from frequent water in the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wheel hub assembly can cause vibrations, noise, and loss of control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Noise emanating from the wheel area

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of suspension and steering components, such as the lower control arm, CV axle, and rotor, can cause loss of control, accidents, or leave the driver stranded.
The failure of electrical and electronic systems, such as door locks, headlights, and key ignition, can cause inconvenience, safety risks, and accidents.
The failure of turbochargers and engine performance issues can cause loss of power, stalling, and accidents.
Poor fit and finish can cause inconvenience, discomfort, and safety risks.
symptoms: poor alignment of doors and panels.
